title: The Townhall Weekend Journal for NOV-01-2013 FRI

The Townhall Weekend Journal for NOV-01-2013 FRI




Friday, November 01, 2013


The Epic Fail of Obamacare




Weekend Journal


Bill Bennett speaks with Rep. Renee Ellmers about the Sebelius hearing.

 Denny Weinberg, a founding of Wellpoint,
    joins Hugh Hewitt to discuss what would fix our health insurance system.

 Dick Cheney discusses foreign policy with Hugh Hewitt.

 Syndicated columnist Charles Krauthammer talks politics on The Dennis Prager Show.
